title: Teamspeak 3.1.6 IPA for iOS
description:
This is a older version of the Teamspeak iOS app for people that can't use iOS 6+.

Installation:
Download the torrent.
Download iFunBox.
Connect your iDevice to your computer.
Open iFunBox.
Click Install app on the second top bar on iFunBox.
Find the file in the browser provided by iFunBox.
Once it is installed you will be able to use the app on your iDevice.

Have fun <3
